    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This shield is designed for throwing and has specially designed straps allowing you to unclasp and throw it as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Free-Actions\">free action</a>. Tower shields cannot be throwing shields.</p>\n<p>Neither a shield’s&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Enhancement-Bonus\">enhancement bonus</a>&nbsp;to AC nor its shield spikes apply on your attack or damage rolls.</p>\n<p>A throwing shield can’t be disarmed.</p>",
